      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Washington Water Power COM\npany this morning is connecting its\nrecently laid tracks on Cannon street\nwith the Boone avenue line, putting\nin switches and laying the ties. The\ninner track of the two cuts off a\ncorner inside OF the curb at Cannon\nstreet and Boone avenue.\n\n\nThe double track at present will\nextend but few yards up Cannon\nstreet, affording room for the passing\nof cars on Cannon."
